author: Mariney Seneme
title: Mariney Seneme
text: I loved the clothes, but some are imposible to get because its out of stock. One particular ofer with a top and a legging had 3 prices, and the introductory price was 15.00 i got that but at the check out the price was over 40.00, I was confuse and canceled .Im definely going to be back if I like the quality and I would like to see a more clear price definition.
